## 1. FRAMING CHUẨN — 3 lớp bản thể (KHAI-20260425-05)

**Gatekeeper quote seal 20260425:**
> *"Lớp 1 runtime lineage = L1 EventBus · L2 Mạch HeyNa · L3 SmartLink — xương sống nội sinh. Lớp 2 substrate = iMac/macOS/Node/bash/TypeScript/npm/Jest/filesystem — nền mang thực thi, execution carrier, REPLACEABLE. Lớp 3 external tool = Bridge v2 forensics ONLY."*

### 1.1 Runtime lineage (Lớp 1) — ontology Nauion-native, nội sinh, bất biến

**Nature:** concept. Không đếm bằng byte. Đếm bằng **topology**.

**Materialization:**
- L1 EventBus — intra-cell UI event bus
- L2 Mạch HeyNa — inter-cell SSE transport (`/mach/heyna` + `/phat/nauion`)
- L3 SmartLink — inter-colony + gravitational field transport

**Evidence trong repo (từ GROUND_TRUTH_REPORT 2026-03-05):**
- `src/core/smartlink/` 10 files · **1519/1529 dòng thật (99.3%)**
  - `smartlink.pressure-field.ts` (354 lines) — pressure field routing
  - `smartlink.point.ts` (274 lines) — TouchRecord
  - `smartlink.competition.ts` (271 lines) — DOMINANT/COMPETING/SUPPRESSED/FADING
  - `smartlink.nattimer.ts` (416 lines) — temporal signature + DFS chain detection
- `src/core/events/` — EventBus + 16 Locks (correlationId, causation chain, ULID, idempotency, back-pressure)
- `src/governance/qneu/` — Qiint engine, Permanent Node, first-seed, audit-extractor
- `MACH_HEYNA_FULL_20260416.md` — migration evidence L2

**Key:** "Mượn Node để thành hệ" vi phạm KHAI-20260425-05. Runtime lineage là **concept nội sinh**, materialize **trong** substrate (TS) — không phải **mượn** substrate làm lineage.

### 1.2 Data / state substrate (Lớp 2a) — Nauion-native extensions

**Nature:** data carrier. Extension riêng, semantic thống nhất per SPEC_NGON_NGU v1.2.

**Byte mass trong `src/` (scan HEAD `04f888f`):**

| Ext | Count | Bytes | Role |
|-----|------:|------:|------|
| `.kris` | 19 | 1.28 MB | Memory K-shell persona (historical lineage) |
| `.phieu` | 10 | 277 KB | Runtime state (Q-shell current) |
| `.anc` | 79 | 172 KB | Cell passport / identity |
