| **Tổng** | **167** | **2.00 MB** | — |

### 1.3 Execution substrate (Lớp 2b) — TS/Node host hiện tại, REPLACEABLE

**Nature:** execution carrier. Host hiện tại chọn TypeScript + Node. Có thể thay (Mac→Linux, Node→Deno, bash→zsh) mà Natt-OS vẫn là Natt-OS.

**Byte mass trong `src/` (scan HEAD `04f888f`):**

| Bucket | Count | % | Role |
|--------|------:|--:|------|
| `.ts + .tsx` tổng | 1229 | 100% | **2.81 MB** |
| `< 200 B` (stub/barrel) | 287 | 23% | Cell plumbing placeholder |
| `200 B - 1 KB` (tiny) | 390 | 32% | Barrel exports, port interfaces |
| `1 - 5 KB` (small module) | 382 | 31% | Small bindings |
| `5 - 20 KB` (substantive) | 156 | 13% | Module logic |
| `> 20 KB` (dense logic) | **14** | **1.1%** | Core engines |

**Role breakdown:**
- `@ts-nocheck` typecheck OFF: **109 file** — tech debt, plan riêng (không chặn runtime, không invalidate claim)
- `index.ts` barrel re-exports: 266 file — topology plumbing
- `port / contract binding`: 140 file — cell boundary interface
- `types / interface / entity`: 80 file — schema declaration
- `.keep / .gitkeep` stubs: 62 file — folder structure placeholder
- **engine (logic):** 184 file — core compute
- **service (logic):** 258 file — orchestration

### 1.4 External tool (Lớp 3) — Bridge v2 forensics

**Nature:** external boundary recovery/forensics tool **ONLY**. **KHÔNG** phải kernel protection, **KHÔNG** phải runtime lõi, **KHÔNG** phải internal stack.

**Scope:** nằm ngoài runtime lineage. Không đếm vào substrate coexistence.

